    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伪装的祝福是一款快节奏的第一人称砍杀游戏，您将在其中探索古老的遗迹，与神秘生物战斗，并收集强大的祝福以求生存。滑行、机动并征服您的敌人！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >终极与特殊能力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >伪装的祝福提供基于能力的战斗体验。寻找能力卷轴以解锁如流血、加速或生命偷取等能力，增强您的力量！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/0dfe76b3459f7610cb2713fa252a6087.poster.avif?t=1768400644\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/0dfe76b3459f7610cb2713fa252a6087.webm?t=1768400644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/0dfe76b3459f7610cb2713fa252a6087.mp4?t=1768400644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >墙跑、滑行、冲刺、攀爬</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/75f22d27707e1d4217768dd214e842b9.poster.avif?t=1768400644\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/75f22d27707e1d4217768dd214e842b9.webm?t=1768400644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/75f22d27707e1d4217768dd214e842b9.mp4?t=1768400644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >增强道具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从普通到英雄级别，增强您的优势与劣势。您可以通过自定义的增强道具或完全随机的选项创建独特的跑步路线和构建。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/e4a324996e8aa587f6160f3b01d13d55.poster.avif?t=1768400644\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/e4a324996e8aa587f6160f3b01d13d55.webm?t=1768400644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/e4a324996e8aa587f6160f3b01d13d55.mp4?t=1768400644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器皮肤</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喜欢展示您的武器皮肤收藏吗？通过击败敌人，您可以赚取金币购买您喜欢的皮肤。自定义您的武士刀、苦无、短剑或刀鞘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/d095e7fbf82273926e0db611184dab47.poster.avif?t=1768400644\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/d095e7fbf82273926e0db611184dab47.webm?t=1768400644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329210/extras/d095e7fbf82273926e0db611184dab47.mp4?t=1768400644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
